cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an invalid format with octet 256 exceeding 255 will cause configuration rejection and prevent NG interface connection to the AMF.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator server address to an invalid IP format with octet 256 exceeding 255 will cause connection failure to the RF simulator.
du.explanation_zh: 將 RF 模擬器伺服器地址設定為無效的 IP 格式，其中八位元組 256 超過 255，會導致與 RF 模擬器的連接失敗。
